        .col-lg-12.mx-auto
            h2 About
            p.lead
            | The UCHICAGO computational platform is the result of a collaborative effort between the 
            | University of Chicago and the Unversity of California, San Diego. 
            | It leverages software and infrastructure from the ATLAS Midwest Tier2 Center, the
            | Pacific Research Platform, the CHASE-CI project,the SLATE project, Virtual Clusters for Community Computation (VC3) and
            | the Open Science Grid.
